descriptionNullable:
### Context

I've been interested in trading stocks and options for a few years and started collecting time and sales data for option trades. This dataset is a sample of 60k+ option trades recorded from 2017-11-13 to 2019-08-09


### Acknowledgements

This data originated from a trade alert feed.


### Inspiration

I wanted to share my data since I've been collecting it for a while and I don't see many similar data sets in the public domain. Hopefully the community can find interesting ways to analyze and visualize it!
